    "There are many use cases for crypto, and below I list some realistic use cases, but the idea that a digital asset with no other purpose or a use case can replace gold, is not very convincing.",
    "It seems more likely that Bitcoin will need to be wrapped and transferred to a different chain, where the cost of transactions is much lower, and be used as a payment system, similar to SWIFT.",
    "That could be a real-world use case, and we already have the Algorand Blockchain, which is capable of handling wrapped Bitcoins, and the cost of transactions is very low, while security is high.",
    "Algorand could even enhance the security of Bitcoin.",
    "There will be many other Blockchains that can do the same function."
